title: 25 Cushions to Knit: Fantastic Cushions for Every Room in Your H
description: A collection of 25 stunning cushion designs, split into six lifestyle settings to suit modern-day living. From the raw energy of Urban Cool to the restrained quiet of Modern Minimal, these are accessories that beg to be knitted. The traditional stitches of cable, moss stitch and lace are combined with colour and embellishment to create unique, desirable accessories to complement any home. There are full instructions for each design, with fabulous colour photographs of the finished cushions, plus helpful tips throughout the book to help make every project a success. These quick-to-knit projects offer knitters of all abilities the opportunity to create spectacular accessories that push the boundaries of traditional hand-knitting.
